channel.title: Quick question
channel.description: Uhh yeah so I don't need help but I wanna ask what's the best source to start with? I've already worked with Pi and delta and I love delta more but there all of the releases are ugly, but I've also grown very fond with sanity's Project Insanity... Anyone know the best source to start with out of those 2? Or if not those 2 shards/hyperion would be fine just would anyone let me know??
